➜钱枫黄磊沈腾都躲不过的命运诅咒！竟然是…
http://www.sohu.com/a/331109124_407929	37002
<p class="ql-align-justify">昨天建军节，钱枫发了一组自己军人时期的照片，又瘦又高又帅，引起了微博一阵轰动。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190802/a86febd0b15240e58f4ea082e7aa7a2f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">网友又动作迅速地翻出钱枫年轻时当演员的照片，棱角分明轮廓锋利，甚至有一点张继科的感觉。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190802/9b358fbb97c54b2fa8d23f9430deba0f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">和现在放飞自己沉迷美食的他一对比，简直是减肥女孩拿来做壁纸警醒自己的最佳神器有没有啊！！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190802/3f990c7d3c1445e4a05c2058650688e1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">随着年纪增长，肥肉和老态也在一寸一寸的侵蚀帅哥，这样的例子并不少见，最最出名就是黄磊老师和小李子。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">一个是长发文艺王子，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190802/6739c6db8342455096f6bd6d0790be4f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">一个是深情“小流氓”Jack，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190802/8a04f7ca1cf74abc91dbed19aaaf34ac.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">然而都无一例外地变身泯然众人的中年老大叔，哎……</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190802/e945c384591542d8921106518cb37bf5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190802/9d6f606b301b4afebda07b85455da5aa.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">另一位代表张卫健，也经历了差不多的命运，年轻的时候也是帅到没朋友。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190802/4cf6dacb3b6e417f92b00660e56fc233.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190802/47ae4ddc06de402aaf8710efbb99d768.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">直到他不知道为什么老是迷恋一些一言难尽的发型，一切就开始变得无法挽回。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190802/e2fed0bc77764c5f8a26fc9820f288a7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">时间的恐怖之处就在于，它能让你面目全非。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">比如我不说你知道下面这位小帅哥是谁吗？</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190802/5b0c906cd7464e21956f4cd7a42a5c61.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">他的名字叫沈腾。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190802/d63a1e0f6915479680b0fd1c717e9ade.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">没错，就是你知道的那位沈腾，没想到吧~~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190802/939622aec87347a68d786565b3947950.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">还有当年的小鲜肉沙溢，（突然好奇现在的小鲜肉们20年后长啥样？？？）</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190802/d5a5ab6615544f5695b9fd7d6f2ac681.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">风华正茂的发哥，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190802/b0426c7f141a4c40a6eba949de0c31cc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">意气风发的星爷，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190802/d8d16fef67ee4e3884b121701826f476.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">以及没有女生可以拒绝的陈冠希，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190802/e326846830d4460aa8bd294d8a11856c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">属于随便一个笑都可以把我秒成渣渣系列。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190802/65f9e98021f643458af8af3cc10e623d.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">然而无情的岁月让他成为爱迪赵本山……</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190802/aa50069ca03b4f5895538f0eb237aaaf.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">作为当年唯二可以hold住泡面头的美男子（另一个是小哇），焦恩俊也是极其能打的颜。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190802/cc09f187e8b546c8bf536127d1816b0b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">他也是史上最帅二郎神，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190802/6d50cdde1d2746f7a159ea4b5c92979e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">然而上次他去创造101找女儿的时候就没有当年俊俏了。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190802/5eb7de0a520a4e60830bfe6cf4b4dea2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">还有陈浩民，他的悟空和哪吒都是我对叛逆男友的最初想象，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190802/95395cb72d82486c9f64235d787df1ba.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">但他却走上了油腻的不归路。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190802/8147b36b1ffe421097f66b50763b3a30.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">娱乐圈公认的花美男金城武，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190802/a3ead49816264cfc9d28aee1dac2ffad.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">据说是梁朝伟唯一承认比自己帅的男明星。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190802/9563197dd3be459abd27ece70ef1ecc6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">在《摆渡人》里面再相遇的两个人却成了这副模样……</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190802/20d7ed3e4da14ab095fae098a746600e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">说到这里，平平无奇古天乐也必须拥有姓名。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190802/efaa9cf680074cc79f89d725498aa059.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">然而这些年来……</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">？？？</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190802/d535a20fe2e24c3b9ae935d4034f745c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">还有前几天微博屠榜的“没有流量”周杰伦。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190802/f0a6243034ba48279b2106c5adb5cde5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">褪去青涩后也曾一身腱子肉，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190802/c6d969d1cd334e859085dfab6a45075d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">然而当他用腱子肉成功泡到老婆之后……</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190802/e102eaa048b0480a895bd58a48a4aeae.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">昆凌哭着说，男人的肌肉都是骗人的。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190802/c85f661ce30b4c479f22f74356a3efb0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">婚后发胖还有陈思诚先生。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190802/cf1120a1641e4a76beb9d3243e135691.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">谁还记得他年轻的模样？？</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190802/f98149d9e22741abb8bf3126426be58a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">以及莫名其妙僵脸的赵又廷。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190802/d133e33cff9f4644ad7cdb05904dce0f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">这还是我当年帅得惊动四海八荒的姑父吗？？？</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190802/f07e2f9673724bff9e8377db54d41be1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">其实说了这么多，并不是真的想吐槽这些明星变丑了。美少年不复当年模样，有的的确是为生活所迫，但也有的人是想摆脱“偶像派”的包袱，为了转型主动变丑。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">更何况，老去本来就是每个人无论美丑都要经历的，这也是为什么我们不断追忆当年，觉得青春可贵。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190802/74716186a8744450845e272f143486bc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">再退一步说，就算是明星也没有义务当你一辈子的梦中情人啊，他有自己的生活，应该让他们自己在颜值和生活舒适度之间找到平衡点。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">毕竟对于看一部剧换一个老公的我们来说，他们不能永远当我的帅男友没关系，反正永远有人当我的帅男友啊~~~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190802/8097c024317f4ace9613fd68eb6b5929.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>